A designer asks you to change the header text from "Dashboard" to "My Dashboard" in a React project. Where do you look?

```jsx
function Header({ user, notifications }) {
  const unread = notifications.filter(n => !n.read);

  return (
    <header className="app-header">
      <h1>Dashboard</h1>
      <span>{user.name}</span>
      <span>{unread.length} new</span>
    </header>
  );
}
```
